### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Validator runtime smoke tests
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@correlationId = 1b8cf017c05479260df1c6ad2a21c707

### Active validator runtime for the default scope
GET {{baseUrl}}/runtime/validator/active?scope_kind=global&scope_key=default
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

###

### Active ingestion bindings bootstrap for consumer/emulator on the default scope
### The response should include `binding`, `fields` and compact runtime metadata.
GET {{baseUrl}}/runtime/ingestion/bindings?scope_kind=global&scope_key=default
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

###

### Latest validation results for the default scope
### After `make up-dataplane` and one active config, the emulator should produce both
### a valid and an invalid sample within a few seconds.
GET {{baseUrl}}/runtime/validator/results?scope_kind=global&scope_key=default&limit=10
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}
